dct_title_s: Tourist map of Andaman & Nicobar Islands.
dct_description_sm: Title from cover. Includes text, indexes, and color illustrations. Includes district, tahsil boundaries. Location map on page two of cover. "Reg. no. 149-NA/SPL-500-2013."
